      "text": "Every morning, before breakfast, Leo opened his bedroom door.\n\nAnd every morning…\n\nPip was already waiting.\n\nWearing his tiny yellow backpack.\n\nSmiling.\n\n\"Ready?\" asked Pip.\n\nLeo grinned.\n\n\"I wonder what adventure we'll find today.\""
    },
    {
      "id": "page-02",
      "scene": {
        "id": "scene-02",
        "background": { "id": "hallway-door", "category": "background" },
