            "id": "pip-look",
            "asset": { "id": "whisper-bubble", "category": "speech-bubble" },
            "position": { "x": 72, "y": 45 },
            "text": "Look!"
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "mixed"
      },
      "text": "Halfway there…\n\nPip stopped.\n\nHis big eyes grew even bigger.\n\nOn the floor sat a tiny green Lego brick.\n\n\"Look!\" whispered Pip.\n\nLeo picked it up carefully.\n\n\"I've been looking for this!\""
    },
    {
      "id": "page-04",
      "scene": {
        "id": "scene-04",
        "background": { "id": "leo-bedroom", "category": "background" },
        "characters": [
          {
            "id": "leo-04",
            "character": "leo",
            "pose": "reaching",
            "expression": "curious",
            "position": "left"
          },
          {
            "id": "pip-04",
            "character": "pip",
            "pose": "floating",
            "expression": "curious",
            "position": "right"
          }
        ],
        "props": [
          {
            "id": "spaceship-04",
            "asset": { "id": "spaceship", "category": "prop" },
            "position": "center",
            "transform": { "scale": 1.2, "zIndex": 12 }
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "narration"
      },
      "text": "\"The spaceship!\" said Leo.\n\n\"It needs one more wing.\"\n\nThey hurried to Leo's room.\n\nLeo clicked the green brick into place.\n\nPip stepped back.\n\n\"It still looks a little wobbly.\"\n\nLeo nodded.\n\n\"It needs balancing.\""
    },
