            "asset": { "id": "sparkle", "category": "effect" },
            "position": { "x": 60, "y": 40 },
            "animation": { "id": "sparkle-anim", "preset": "sparkle" }
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "narration"
      },
      "text": "\"What if…\" said Pip slowly.\n\n\"…spaceships had two extra wings?\"\n\nLeo's eyes lit up.\n\n\"They'd fly even better!\"\n\nSoon there were bricks everywhere.\n\nBlue bricks. Grey bricks. Tiny transparent windows. Long white rockets.\n\nThe spaceship grew bigger and bigger."
    },
    {
      "id": "page-06",
      "scene": {
        "id": "scene-06",
        "background": { "id": "leo-bedroom-spaceship", "category": "background" },
