            "position": { "x": 50, "y": 70 },
            "transform": { "scale": 1.5, "zIndex": 10 }
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "narration"
      },
      "text": "Just then…\n\n\"Meeooow.\"\n\nWhiskers the cat squeezed into the cardboard spaceship box.\n\nLeo laughed.\n\n\"The captain has arrived!\"\n\nPip saluted.\n\n\"Captain Whiskers!\"\n\nThe cat purred proudly."
    },
    {
      "id": "page-08",
      "scene": {
        "id": "scene-08",
