            "character": "pip",
            "pose": "floating",
            "expression": "excited",
            "position": "right"
          },
          {
            "id": "whiskers-08",
            "character": "whiskers",
            "pose": "in-box",
            "expression": "content",
            "position": { "x": 55, "y": 75 },
            "transform": { "scale": 1.2, "zIndex": 20 }
          }
        ],
        "effects": [
          {
            "id": "giggle-08",
            "asset": { "id": "giggle-lines", "category": "effect" },
            "position": { "x": 50, "y": 30 },
            "animation": { "id": "giggle-anim", "preset": "float" }
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "narration"
      },
      "text": "\"If Whiskers is flying to the Moon…\" said Pip, \"…what will he eat?\"\n\nLeo thought very hard.\n\n\"Moon fish?\"\n\n\"Space biscuits?\"\n\n\"Cheese?\"\n\nBoth of them burst into giggles."
    },
    {
      "id": "page-09",
      "scene": {
        "id": "scene-09",
        "background": { "id": "leo-bedroom-spaceship", "category": "background" },
        "characters": [
          {
