            "id": "spaceship-09",
            "asset": { "id": "spaceship", "category": "prop" },
            "position": { "x": 45, "y": 65 },
            "transform": { "scale": 1.4, "zIndex": 11 }
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "narration"
      },
      "text": "Dad appeared at the bedroom door.\n\nHe smiled when he saw the enormous spaceship.\n\n\"It looks amazing.\"\n\nLeo beamed.\n\n\"We found the green brick!\"\n\n\"And then Captain Whiskers…\"\n\n\"And then…\"\n\nLeo stopped.\n\nDad smiled gently.\n\n\"Weren't you heading somewhere first?\"\n\nLeo blinked.\n\n\"I was?\""
    },
    {
      "id": "page-10",
      "scene": {
        "id": "scene-10",
        "background": { "id": "leo-bedroom-spaceship", "category": "background" },
        "characters": [
          {
            "id": "leo-10",
            "character": "leo",
            "pose": "slippers",
            "expression": "gentle",
            "position": "center",
            "transform": { "zIndex": 30 }
          },
          {
            "id": "pip-10",
            "character": "pip",
            "pose": "floating",
            "expression": "gentle",
            "position": "right"
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "narration"
      },
      "text": "Leo looked around the room.\n\nThe spaceship. The cat. The bricks. The cardboard box.\n\nThen he looked down.\n\nHe was still wearing his slippers.\n\n\"Oh!\" he whispered.\n\n\"My shoes.\""
    },
    {
      "id": "page-11",
      "scene": {
        "id": "scene-11",
        "background": { "id": "leo-bedroom", "category": "background" },
        "characters": [
          {
            "id": "leo-11",
            "character": "leo",
            "pose": "bust",
            "expression": "gentle",
            "position": "left"
          },
          {
            "id": "pip-11",
            "character": "pip",
            "pose": "puzzled",
            "expression": "gentle",
            "position": "right"
          },
          {
            "id": "dad-11",
            "character": "dad",
            "pose": "kneeling",
            "expression": "gentle",
            "position": "far-right",
            "transform": { "scale": 0.85, "zIndex": 10 }
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "narration"
      },
      "text": "\"I thought I'd only stopped for a tiny moment.\"\n\nDad nodded.\n\n\"I know.\"\n\nLeo looked puzzled.\n\n\"It still feels like a tiny moment.\"\n\nPip looked puzzled too.\n\n\"It felt tiny to me as well.\"\n\nNobody was cross.\n\nEverybody was thinking."
    },
    {
