            "pose": "backpack-zipped",
            "expression": "gentle",
            "position": "right"
          },
          {
            "id": "dad-12",
            "character": "dad",
            "pose": "winking",
            "expression": "smiling",
            "position": "far-right",
            "transform": { "scale": 0.85, "zIndex": 10 }
          }
        ],
        "objects": [
          {
            "id": "green-brick-12",
            "asset": { "id": "green-brick", "category": "object" },
            "position": { "x": 78, "y": 68 },
            "transform": { "scale": 0.7, "zIndex": 35 }
          }
        ],
        "dialogue": "narration"
      },
      "text": "Dad picked up the little green brick.\n\nHe placed it gently into Pip's tiny backpack.\n\n\"Looks like today's adventure started here.\"\n\nLeo smiled.\n\n\"It was a really good adventure.\"\n\nPip smiled too.\n\n\"It was.\"\n\nDad winked.\n\n\"And next time…\"\n\nLeo laughed.\n\n\"…maybe the shoes can come first.\"\n\nPip zipped up the backpack.\n\nAnother adventure. Another treasure. Another story to remember."
    }
  ]
